<text top="88" left="90" width="60" height="14" font="13"><b>S/PV.5579 </b></text>
<text top="93" left="453" width="3" height="14" font="0"> </text>
<text top="109" left="90" width="3" height="14" font="0"> </text>
<text top="1081" left="787" width="44" height="12" font="14">06-64481 </text>
<text top="1081" left="90" width="10" height="14" font="13"><b>4 </b></text>
<text top="1096" left="90" width="3" height="14" font="13"><b> </b></text>
<text top="132" left="90" width="365" height="17" font="3">one party at the expense of another. This must be kept </text>
<text top="150" left="90" width="292" height="17" font="3">in mind when the resolution is implemented. </text>
<text top="177" left="90" width="7" height="17" font="3"> </text>
<text top="177" left="126" width="331" height="17" font="3">I now resume my functions as President of the </text>
<text top="195" left="90" width="59" height="17" font="3">Council. </text>
<text top="132" left="468" width="10" height="17" font="3"> </text>
<text top="132" left="504" width="334" height="17" font="3">The Security Council has thus concluded the </text>
<text top="150" left="468" width="368" height="17" font="3">present stage of its consideration of the item on its </text>
<text top="168" left="468" width="351" height="17" font="3">agenda. The Council will remain seized of the matter. </text>
<text top="195" left="468" width="4" height="17" font="5"><i> </i></text>
<text top="195" left="495" width="202" height="17" font="5"><i>  The meeting rose at 4.35 p.m. </i></text>
<text top="213" left="468" width="4" height="17" font="3"> </text>
</page>
